here is a chronology of the eightyear war between iran and 
iraq which remains formally unresolved pending a final peace 
treaty 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
april 1 ayatollah ruhollah khomeini who returned to tehran in 
february after the shah was toppled proclaims the islamic republic 
of iran 
july 16 saddam hussein vice chairman of iraqs ruling 
revolutionary command council replaces ahmed hassan albakr as 
president 
nov4 us embassy in tehran is stormed by militants 
fiftytwo americans are held hostage for 444 days 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
installations on the iraqi side of shattalarab 
sept 2023 iraqi warplanes strike tehran airport army begins 
advance and later reaches karun river several hundred miles into 
iran 
sept 28 un security council adopts resolution 479 calling 
for a ceasefire iran rejects the call 
</TEXT>
