holdings into us assets is that they can get good prices 
restrict this repatriation of capital and the us economy will 
lose one of the few energetic factors left in it 
the united states is not going to provide for its economic 
future by halting investment that gives foreigners a stake in 
keeping the us economy healthy the united states will provide 
for its future by getting its own house in order 
