impairment and that her case was an appeal to public fears about 
flying with drunken pilots 
what we have in this case is stealth impairment mauzy said 
impairment that hasnt been detected 
kirchner 36 of highland ranch colo captain norman lyle 
prouse 51 of conyers ga and flight engineer joseph balzer 35 
of antioch tenn have been on trial since july 25 on charges of 
